headline.main: SPACE ARK GOES ON 3-DAY FLIGHT; Insects and Plants Launched in Biological Research

results.snippet: CAPE KENNEDY, Fla., Sept. 7 (UPI)--A biological research laboratory carrying thousands of insects and plants soared into orbit today on a three-day flight to see what biological risks men may take on long journeys into space.

results.abstract: Surveyor 5 shut down for 2-wk lunar night after televising 18,006 pictures

headline.main: Surveyor Shut Off For Lunar Night; Sent 18,006 Photos

results.snippet: PASADENA, Calif., Sept. 24 (AP) Surveyor 5 was shut down today for the two-weeklong lunar night after televising 18,006 pictures more than the combined output of two previous Surveyor spacecraft.
